This instruction for Fedora 30

# dnf install ibus-unikey \
terminal: konsolar \
# ibus-setup \
in <Input Method> panel
click: Add \
find: Vietnamese -> Unikey \
click: Add \

# set ibus-unikey run automaticaly when starting os \
press window on keyboard \
find key word: Autostart \
On the Autostart panel: \
click Add Program -> guid to (/usr/bin/ibus-daemon) where ibus-unikey was installed \
click OK
NOTE: status: Enabled
